data.description: Boaters will love this location!!! Just one bridge and it's a straight shot to the river and the gulf. Come check out this 3/2 pool home in SE Cape. The home has had a new roof this year. The pool was resurfaced, has a new pool pump, heat pump, salt generator and freshly painted pool cage all done in 2023. In addition, there is a newer AC, tankless hot water heater and an electrical panel and grounds. The home is equipped with impact windows/doors/garage door throughout and electric shutters on the back lanai for storm protection for French doors. Enjoy sitting out by the pool or on your dock, watching the sunsets and the manatees and dolphins play in the canal. This home is waiting for you to come and live your Florida waterfront dream.
